## 11Ô∏è‚É£ Release Plan
| Phase | Duration | Deliverables |
|--------|-----------|--------------|
| **Phase 1 ‚Äî Chatbot MVP** | 6 weeks | Google Chat integration, Bedrock KB, logging, guardrails, feedback |
| **Phase 2 ‚Äî Agent Mode** | +8 weeks | Action Groups, tool Lambdas, RBAC, approvals, audit dashboard |
| **Phase 3 ‚Äî Analytics & Insights** | +6 weeks | Manager dashboards, sentiment analysis, reporting API |

---

## 12Ô∏è‚É£ Risks & Mitigation
| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|---------|------------|
| Hallucination / wrong answers | Medium | RAG + citations + feedback loop |
| Unauthorized access | High | IAM least privilege + RBAC |
| Cost spike | Medium | Token trimming + usage dashboards |
| Poor KB quality | Medium | HR/IT curation workflow |
| Low adoption | Medium | Pilot launch + awareness training |

---

## 13Ô∏è‚É£ Dependencies
- AWS Bedrock access (Claude 3.5 Sonnet)  
- Google Cloud workspace project + bot registration  
- IAM roles & policies for Lambdas  
- GitHub repo sync workflow to S3  
- Security review sign-off  

